  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Before you begin...</strong></p><p>Get all your ingredients and equipment ready</p><p>Skim through these steps, then wash your fruit and veg</p><p>Note: Equipment and pan sizes vary. Make sure you cook food thoroughly (even if it takes you a little longer than 10 min)</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Now, let's get started!</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>mayo</strong>,<strong> smoked paprika</strong>,<strong> oregano</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>cider vinegar</strong> to a small bowl</p><p>Add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>peri peri mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the<strong> sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> finely</p><p>Cut the <strong>lime<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half</p><p>Cut 1/2<span class=\"text-danger\"> [1]</span><strong> lime</strong> into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> wedges</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained sweetcorn</strong> and <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>juice</strong> of the <strong>lime half<span class=\"text-danger\">[ves]</span></strong> (save the wedges for later!) and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong>, give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>sweetcorn salsa</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut the<strong> avocado<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half lengthways, around the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p><p>Remove the stone<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a teaspoon</p><p>Scoop the <strong>avocado</strong> out of the skin<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> using a spoon and slice it finely, lengthways</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non stick) over a high heat</p><p>Cut the <strong>halloumi</strong> into 12 <span class=\"text-danger\">[24]</span> slices</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi slices</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min on each side or until golden</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> tortillas</strong> to a plate</p><p>Put the plate in the <strong>microwave</strong> and cook for 1-2 min, or until warmed through (alternatively, add the tortillas to a baking tray and put them in the oven for 2-3 min!)</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/halloumi-tacos-with-peri-peri-mayo/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> golden halloumi</strong> to the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> sweetcorn salsa</strong> and<strong> sliced avocado</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the<strong> peri peri mayo</strong> and serve the<strong> lime wedges</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
